name: Cooped Up (itch) (egerdone, kazningo, darrmander, Axel Björnsson)
name_original: Cooped Up (itch) (egerdone, kazningo, darrmander, Axel Björnsson)
description:
Cooped Up (itch) (egerdone, kazningo, darrmander, Axel Björnsson) is a platformer game developed by kazningo, egerdone and darrmander. It was originally released in 2018.
You can play Cooped Up (itch) (egerdone, kazningo, darrmander, Axel Björnsson) on PC. You can purchase the game on itch.io.
